Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,還真少見  居然連社長都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學  你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是內卷學長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,還問我在幹什麼  難道看不出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是完全看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她是一年級的可蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,人如其名  是位外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不過小時候因為父母的工作而來到了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,已經在這裡生活6到7年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然半年前她父母回國了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不過可蕾特因為已經適應了這邊的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(782,660)}locket
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此  是要找吊墜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我還真沒看出來你是在找東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒那麼厲害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是誇你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷學長也幫我找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面有著我非常重要的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很重要的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特  爸爸和媽媽要回國了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己一個人會不會很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心  只要有這張照片的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就能感到你們一直都在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙吧  那吊墜是怎樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}註：日語中火箭和吊墜讀音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是不會飛的那種吊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,首先我們先去失物認領處看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,造個好箱子哇  鎌倉幕府
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}註：いい箱（1185）作ろう鎌倉幕府  日語裡面用「好箱子」諧音「1185」用來記憶鎌倉幕府成立時間  早期曾經用\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h「いい国（1192）作ろう鎌倉幕府」（建個好國家吧鎌倉幕府）後來時間統一成西曆1185年  故有此說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,人家很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是小山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  你們關係真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\fsp10\bord0\shad0\c&H1D1920&\pos(526,351)\frz298.5}您要不要也進入\N這個世界看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs30\fsp3\bord0\shad0\c&H1D1920&\pos(599,442)\frz30.11}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學  找吊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,差點忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺大家的失物真是五花八門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,學長  這是宇佐美學姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,居然還丟東西  宇佐美學姐還真冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗圆_GBK\fs55\fax0.2\bord3\c&H4CD0EF&\3c&H403427&\shad0\frz355.3\pos(738,524)}失物招領處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗圆_GBK\fs23\bord1\c&H4CD0EF&\3c&H403427&\shad0\b0\pos(591,166)}失物招領處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不過最關鍵的吊墜不在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話  只好老老實實來找了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學還記得你今天去過哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…今天上學後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,先上了天台放風箏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然後被老師發現後狠狠地教育了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,然後被拉去指導室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你都幹什麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我是昨天就知道吊墜不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  那你昨天去過哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你如此深入調查我的行動模式到底有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不幫你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是內卷和可蕾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  丟東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我撿到了嗎  謝謝可蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  吊墜不見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  雖然我很想幫你  但是值日生的工作還沒做完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這個我剛剛在走廊上撿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這是社長的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  如果他來活動室了  麻煩你們交給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,髮夾變成念珠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就像稻草富翁那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,用所持的東西與每次遇到的人交換  讓所持的東西越來越好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,最後獲得了巨大的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因為髮夾變成了念珠  或許社長撿到了吊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是積極的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,機會主義!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪?  什麼時候不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是宇佐美同學撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  待會得跟她說聲謝謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要給什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,吊墜  你撿到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,稻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草市長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是稻草市長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\bord3.5\shad0\c&HD97C53&\3c&H824A35&\frz273.2\move(910,160,910,180)\fade(0,210)}打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,身為社長  卻完全派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這跟是不是社長沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這下該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就算問我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只好老老實實地找了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此地毯式尋找也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那一定不是掉了  而是被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那吊墜是怎樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那你昨天去過哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.84,Comment,,0,0,0,,就算問我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我對你們倆的信任嚴重受創
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再裝下去也沒用  還是坦白從寬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  吊墜就不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你口袋裡有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼把口袋翻過來  然後再把手攤開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你那不自然的握拳是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,魔術表演時間!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好  吊墜盒現在瞬間移動到了我的手裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你也太煞費苦心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,它原本就裝在口袋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,按照傳統  我會切腹的  為我介錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}註：「介錯」是出自日本歷史上為切腹者來擔當補刀行為之人的稱謂  就是斬首  以讓切腹者更快死亡  免除痛苦折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不過找到了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是你重要的家人照片吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可別再弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷學長真是溫柔!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這種自然流露的溫柔攻陷了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,家人的照片?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?  裡面裝的難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你說這很重要  我便滿以為是你遠方父母的照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,上週拍的大頭貼!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然是自己?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体 第二版\fs30\bord0\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HF0E5D4&\b0\frz356.6\pos(941.428,645.715)}失物招領
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs40\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(945.428,377.715)\frz287.6}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs30\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz12.63\pos(978.428,410.715)}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒來!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒來還沒來還沒來!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,難得來一次  可大家都還沒來!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,無聊死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,無聊死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果撿鞋不用手  就算我贏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  可蕾特同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美學姐  你來得太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  和班上的同學聊著聊著就來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都已經糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,社長怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,睡覺的又不一定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是因為作畫不順利  情緒正低落著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,都這樣一整天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…不會有事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,社長就這麼一直醒著…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,擔心的是這個?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我說啊  我也是有過一整天醒著的日子的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你終於成長了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.97,Comment,,0,0,0,,你是在看不起我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:28.60,Comment,,0,0,0,,不不  怎麼可能呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了?  瓶頸期了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,該說是遇到瓶頸了呢  還是說才思枯竭呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我在構思我的新老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可就是想不到一個好髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,髮型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那  比如說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,短髮波波頭…之類的…怎麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(445,660)}short bob
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣的髮型啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我來告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  別的啊  可蕾!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不該提這茬的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這哪位啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,壽和鮑勃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(575,660)}Shou
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(685,660)}Bob
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷學長  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是壽和鮑勃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是禿著頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  反正我也不抱期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:24.07,Comment,,0,0,0,,我試著迎合了宇佐美學姐的口味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.36,Comment,,0,0,0,,就這幅壽和鮑勃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.95,Comment,,0,0,0,,挺不錯的  光頭女生有意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他還是喜歡這種類型的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:33.06,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\shad0\c&H688D1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fade(0,500)}妹妹在看著你哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,昴哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,請收下我的心吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那就明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,再見!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H4839BE&\frz358.2\move(373,456,373,616)}可愛迷人的\N美髮特集!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去參考參考
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太謝謝你了  我會好好參考的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,隨你參考好啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷學長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也別忘了這個!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,壽和鮑勃就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這並不是短髮波波頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂短髮波波頭就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs40\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1159.428,202.715)\frz273.8\b0}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs30\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz357\pos(1180.428,243.715)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\fsp5\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz292.4\pos(719.428,307.715)\b0}這些都是\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h三次元的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\fsp5\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz17.92\pos(785.428,446.715)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0\frz288\pos(471.428,432.715)}要不然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs35\bord3\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0\frz198.2\pos(507.428,468.715)}…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天去哪裡玩玩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  香織
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天也得去參加社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因為想盡早為下次比賽做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞希正享受著青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我也沒有這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是喜歡畫畫而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡畫畫勝過內卷?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  自然是更喜歡內卷了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  沙耶加  看你讓我說了些什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞希你正享受著青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,以這種淫亂的理由參加社團活動可不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼淫亂呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們今天就去美術社玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?  別來吧別來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊  有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還不是來添亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不會的不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,非社員本來就不被允許來遊玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就作為入社體驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這個主意不錯  就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,放過我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來  沙耶加  你的新聞社怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,今日任務  找大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我們社並沒有什麼新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,從沒有新聞的地方創造新聞  這才叫做大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要這樣偷偷摸摸的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  總覺得好像把怪人帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂  居然把摯友叫成怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞這個壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:19.35,Comment,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這間活動室還挺普通的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我家的瑞希承蒙你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞希是一位心地很善良的好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有些地方挺淫蕩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣好嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,體驗入社?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就是掛著這個名號來蹭玩兒的  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,噓!  涼子  噓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來  今天只有內卷一個人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  社長他們去了屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞我問你喔  我可以畫點東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,涼子和沙耶加也畫吧  我們來比賽!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,畫得最差的要請飲料!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我接受挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那要畫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,主題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,居然來這招…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,表情有點僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,兩位  笑一個笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續保持這樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞你再往右邊靠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,緊緊依偎在內卷的肩上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因為畫不進去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,動作快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就對了嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝我吧  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得  看得我都害羞起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真抱歉  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,居然要你陪我做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那麼接下來就這樣順勢親個嘴兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你先做示範給我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  別這樣  人家還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:23.85,Comment,,0,0,0,,多說無益
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,公佈結果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我要蘋果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我要奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我要茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要喝香蕉歐蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的畫得那麼差嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,危險  危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,香蕉歐蕾賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可樂  給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  內卷不能喝碳酸飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺有點可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這罐我嘴巴碰過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的話要和我的交換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  說實在那有點太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯你個頭  那罐是人家喝過的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,換句話說  就是間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,間?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,間接接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,太遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,香織你也說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來是開開玩笑而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那罐明明是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  我全都喝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷  那罐是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來我們就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?  你看起來好像也不怎麼不甘心耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?  沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好受打擊哇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  秀恩愛的你們快給我爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是間接的  但是也是接過吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,香織她們今天過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沙耶加!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真不好意思  我居然在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,作為處罰我到走廊上罰站
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我才想問好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不是什麼可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是美術社的顧問  立花夢子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是說不把我當作顧問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛似乎有點像老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:23:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是不良少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.43,0:23:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好  好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.02,0:24:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我去外面吸一下新鮮空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.48,0:24:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有變態!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  這個美術社大有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微去散步  敬請期待
